== 製作 ==
艾爾文·溫克勒和羅伯特·查托夫打算1972年的電影《龍虎鐵金剛》重啟。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌報導，2009年2月的[[柏林影展|柏林影展]]宣布獲得重啟的版權；三個月後宣布，由[[賽門·衛斯特|賽門·衛斯特]]執導與[[傑森·史塔森|傑森·史塔森]]主演<ref>{{cite journal | last=McNary | first=Dave | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118003364 | title=West gives 'Mechanic' an overhaul | journal=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2009-05-07 | access-date=2015-03-07 | archive-date=2012-11-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107120410/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118003364 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年10月，[[班·佛斯特|班·佛斯特]]和[[唐納·蘇德蘭|唐納·蘇德蘭]]加入本片與史塔森一起參與演出<ref>{{cite journal | last=Kroll | first=Justin | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118009959 | title=Ben Foster, Donald Sutherland | journal=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=2009-10-14 | access-date=2015-03-07 | archive-date=2012-11-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107120436/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118009959 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。主要拍攝於10月14日在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的[[紐奧良|紐奧良]]進行歷時九週的拍攝<ref>{{cite news | last=Scott | first=Mike | url=http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2009/10/hollywood_south_is_heating_up.html | title=Hollywood South is heating up as the weather cools down | work=The Times-Picayune | date=2009-10-26 | accessdate=2015-03-07 | archive-date=2017-12-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216121420/http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2009/10/hollywood_south_is_heating_up.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。拍攝地點包括[[聖坦曼尼堂區_(路易斯安那州)|聖坦曼尼堂區]]<ref>{{cite news | last=Alexander-Bloch | first=Benjamin | url=http://www.nola.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2009/10/hollywood_comes_to_the_north_s.html | title=Jason Statham back in action locally -- this time in St. Tammany | work=The Times-Picayune | date=2009-10-26 | accessdate=2015-03-07 | archive-date=2017-09-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928145906/http://www.nola.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2009/10/hollywood_comes_to_the_north_s.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>、紐奧良世界貿易中心<ref>{{cite news | last=Scott | first=Mike 